</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-gFmZvT eCWkjm pf-41_ pf-text-1"><strong>Unwell child</strong> - A child experiencing symptoms of illness or distress, ranging from minor ailments to more serious medical conditions.




















