</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-gFmZvT eCWkjm pf-50_ pf-text-1"><strong>Children Act 1989</strong> - Places a duty on local authorities to safeguard and promote the welfare of children in need, including ensuring appropriate medical care and attention.





















